Number::Uncertainty
-------------------  

What is it?
-----------

The module is an object orientated interface to allow a number and an
uncertainty on the number to be stored in one tidy little bundle that
can be passed around

Why do it?
----------

While other, packages a lot like this one are floating around, none do
exactly what required. It was easier to hack out another one than try and
kludge our ideas into the form factor of an existing package.

Provides
--------

The package provides the following classes

    Number::Uncertainty

further information can be found in the POD included in Uncertainty.pm

Where can I get it?
-------------------

The package is availabe from CPAN <http://www.cpan.org/>.

Installation
------------

Installation is automated using the ExtUtils::MakeMaker library

     % perl Makefile.PL
     % make
     % make test
     % make install

Authors
-------

